# poni

Safe Batteries Included Agentic Development

## Summary

Poni is a local-first git-friendly agentic development tool for your entire team.

## Features

- Control agent tool usage with policies (prevent destructive calls).
- Define agentic tools.
- Auto-generate and maintain consistent documentation.
- Organize your team's shared development memory.

### Premium Features

- Usage audit
- One-click integration setup
- Pre-configured role-based policies

## CLI

- `poni init` - Initialize poni in the current directory.
- `poni serve` - ...
- `poni run PROMPT` - ...
- `poni docs` - Generate documentation for your repository.
- `poni auth` - Authenticate with our server for premium and enterprise features.

## Details

Poni is a CLI tool and MCP server that provides governance, shared knowledge, and team tooling for agentic development.
It acts as the complete control plane for AI agents in development workflows.


